WEBVTT

00:00.537 --> 00:01.706
Previously on "The Originals"...

00:01.706 --> 00:04.733
Our community is under attack.

00:04.734 --> 00:06.103
They're
declaring war on us.

00:06.105 --> 00:07.623
All his life,
there's only ever been

00:07.624 --> 00:09.124
one man he has
truly feared...

00:09.125 --> 00:10.826
My father Mikael.

00:10.827 --> 00:11.794
All we need is a witch

00:11.795 --> 00:12.928
who could help us
find him.

00:12.929 --> 00:14.862
- Celeste.
- How did you know?

00:14.864 --> 00:16.297
If you have come here
seeking revenge...

00:16.299 --> 00:17.716
Oh, I'll have
my revenge,

00:17.717 --> 00:18.783
starting with Klaus.

00:18.784 --> 00:20.803
He is gonna know
pain and torment

00:20.804 --> 00:22.254
like he's never
felt before.

00:22.255 --> 00:25.307
Then that leaves Rebekah,
your tragic sister.

00:25.308 --> 00:26.458
She's about
to find herself

00:26.459 --> 00:27.976
in quite
the predicament.

00:28.402 --> 00:30.113
Genevieve knows
where your sister is,

00:30.279 --> 00:31.463
Bastiana has Klaus

00:31.464 --> 00:32.898
tucked away
someplace safe.

00:33.324 --> 00:35.243
I guess always isn't
forever after all.

