01:37.997 --> 01:40.164
Who's there?

02:15.751 --> 02:17.618
How the hell did I get here?

02:33.268 --> 02:36.521
Genevieve.

02:36.522 --> 02:37.973
Rebekah.

02:37.974 --> 02:40.142
Tell me you're not
leaving already.

02:40.143 --> 02:41.953
I thought we
might reminisce.

03:11.014 --> 03:15.904
Sync & corrections by <font color="#00ff00">Rafael UPD</font>
